flowchart TD
    A[Open engine compartment] --> B{Oil dipstick<br/>between marks?}
    B -->|Low| C[Top up with 15W-40]
    B -->|OK| D{Coolant level<br/>in header tank?}
    D -->|Low| E[Top up — check for leaks]
    D -->|OK| F{Raw water strainer<br/>clear?}
    F -->|Dirty| G[Unscrew lid, clean basket]
    F -->|Clear| H{Belt tension<br/>& wear OK?}
    H -->|Loose/frayed| I[Report to charter base]
    H -->|OK| J[Seacock open?<br/>Check raw-water intake]
    J --> K[Start engine]
    K --> L{Water from<br/>exhaust within<br/>20 seconds?}
    L -->|No| M[STOP ENGINE<br/>No cooling = damage in minutes]
    L -->|Yes| N[Let idle 2 min, then OK to use]
